title: Syllabus mentioned in ERP
text: Prerequisite : Nil RS coupling, CFT, Tanabe-Sugano diagram, Ligand field theory, molecular orbital theory. Magnetic and spectral properties of coordination compounds. Inorganic reaction mechanism- substitution, electron transfer, photochemical reactions. Books: B.N. Figgis, J.E Huheey, P.W. Atkins
